channel.title: For Sale brand new Axoloti board in US
channel.description:
Hi Guys,
I am selling a brand new Axoloti board I purchased and never used. While I was waiting for this board to arrive I found a second board used so I never used this new board when it arrived. It was never even pulled from anti static bag. You will be getting a As New board. With exchange rate I paid $88. Please send me an offer. I am in Los Angeles if someone is local or willing to ship anywhere in the USA. Please send me a message if interested.
Thanks
